Source code for maingui.report_generation

from reportlab.pdfgen import canvas
from reportlab.lib.pagesizes import A4
from reportlab.lib.units import inch
from maingui.settings import Report
from enum import Enum
from abc import ABC, abstractmethod




[docs]class ReportFormats(Enum):
    PDF = 1
    Markdown = 2
    Text = 3




[docs]class ReportGenerator(ABC):

    def __init__(self, report: Report, filename: str):
        self.report = report
        self.filename = filename
        self._c = canvas.Canvas(self.filename, pagesize=A4)
        super().__init__()


[docs]    def generate_report(self):
        self.report_header("RF Forensics Report")
        self.report_results()
        self.report_footer()
        self.report_signoff()
        self.save_report()

    def report_header(self, heading):
        pass

[docs]    @abstractmethod

        pass



[docs]    def save_report(self):
        self._c.showPage()
        self._c.save()




[docs]class ForensicsReport(ReportGenerator):

    def __init__(self, report: Report, filename: str):
        super().__init__(report, filename)

        self.lmargin = 0.3 * inch


[docs]    def report_header(self, heading):
        self._c.setStrokeColorRGB(0, 0, 0)
        self._c.setFillColorRGB(0, 0, 0)
        self._c.setFont("Helvetica", 18)
        self._c.drawString(self.lmargin, 10 * inch, "Forenics Report")
        self._c.drawString(self.lmargin, 11 * inch, heading)



[docs]    def report_subheading(self):
        self._c.setStrokeColorRGB(0, 0, 0)
        self._c.setFillColorRGB(0, 0, 0)
        self._c.setFont("Helvetica", 14)
        self._c.drawString(self.lmargin, 10.5 * inch, f"Technician: {self.report.technician}")
        self._c.drawString(self.lmargin, 10.2 * inch, f"Date: {self.report.date}")



[docs]    def report_results(self):
        pass



[docs]    def report_footer(self):
        self._c.drawString(self.lmargin, 3 * inch, f"Comments: {self.report.comments}")



[docs]    def report_signoff(self):
        self._c.drawString(self.lmargin, 2 * inch, f"Sign-off: {self.report.signoff}")
